Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.88,0:00:11.10,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{A lot of students are dressing up\N for this year's Tsuwabuki Fest.}Lễ hội Tsuwabuki năm nay có\Nnhiều học sinh hoá trang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:12.98,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{It's not unlike Halloween.}Không giống như Halloween.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:18.08,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,{Hey, get out of my way!}Hãy tránh ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:19.82,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Oh, I've seen that exact line...}Mình đã đọc qua cảnh này...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:22.27,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{in light novels before.}trong tiểu thuyết trước đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:36.18,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I've seen this in light novels, too.}Cái này cũng trong tiểu thuyết nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:11.44,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,{I'm really sorry! Are you sure you're okay?}Tớ rất xin lỗi, cậu ổn chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:14.69,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,{Does anything hurt? Any bumps anywhere?}Có đau không? Có bị u ở đâu không?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:17.03,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Uh, well...}À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:22.31,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Thanks for your concern.}Cảm ơn vì đã quan tâm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:24.54,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,{I should be the one thanking you.}Tớ mới là người phải cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.14,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,{You're even carrying half my stuff for me.}Cậu còn phụ tớ mang đồ nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:29.38,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,{Hey, hey!}Này này!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:34.30,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,{Let's walk to the classroom together.}Đi cùng nhau đến lớp học đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:37.07,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,{I've been wanting to talk to you, anyway.}Tớ cũng muốn nói chuyện với cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:42.07,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,{Sosuke and Anna are always talking about you,\N so it almost feels like I know you.}Sosuke và Anna lúc nào cũng nói về cậu\N nên tớ nghĩ mình cũng sẽ thích cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:45.91,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Um, I do talk to Hakamada sometimes, \Nbut it's not like we're really friends.}Tớ có nói chuyện với Hakamada \Nnhưng bảo bạn bè thì hơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:47.85,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,{Oh, really?}Thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.85,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,{Then why don't you become \Nfriends with both of us?}Vậy sao không trở thành bạn với bọn tớ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:51.93,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,{Okay?}Nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:56.48,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Oh, no! She's so dazzling, \Nshe's gonna kill me!}Chết tiệt! Hào quang nữ chính đây mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:03:00.08,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{It's almost like Himemiya-san\N has light affinity.}Giống như Himemiya vậy. Có hào quang rực rỡ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:02.94,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{She definitely has a certain \Nsomething that Yanami doesn't.}Khác hoàn toàn với Yanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:08.87,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{It's like TV, where you think, "Wow, 4K \Nlooks awesome!" And then 8K comes out...}Kiểu như "Ồ cái TV 4K này\N đỉnh quá!" cho đến khi ta thấy 8K...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:10.36,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Oh, it's 4K.}A, 4K kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:11.91,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{For-kay?}4 Kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:13.83,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{No, never mind.}Không có gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.30,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur0.4\fs14\fnArial\b1\fscx90\3c&H4E5652&\c&H0B0C0A&\pos(421.333,259.999)}{Tsuwabuki Fest Is In}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.30,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fnArial\b1\fscx90\blur0.4\fs14\3c&H4E5652&\c&H0B0C0A&\pos(466.667,312.667)}{Days}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.85,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Y-You're late. Where were you?}C-Cậu đến trễ. Làm gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:20.96,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I had a meeting about my class event.}Tớ có buổi họp với lớp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:23.09,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Didn't you have one?}Còn cậu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:25.29,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{N-No.}K-Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:30.31,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Nobody in class told me anything.}Không ai trong lớp nói gì tôi cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:33.45,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{O-Oh. I guess not, then.}À ừm... thế hả.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:36.44,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Try these out.}Ăn thử đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:40.47,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{First, the sugar-coated peanuts\N Natsume Soseki liked so much.}Đậu phộng bọc đường mà \NSoseki Natsume thích đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:44.07,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I gave it a modern update with \Ncocoa powder, so give it a taste.}Tớ đã thử cải tiến bằng bột cacao, ăn đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:49.91,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Oh, yum! D-Did you make this, Nukumizu?}C-Cậu làm nó à? Ngon quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:53.66,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{No, my little sister did. \NSame with the others.}Không, em gái tớ làm. Còn loại khác nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:55.88,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Th-Then what did you do?}V-Vậy cậu làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:58.88,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I washed dishes and gave her\N shoulder massages and stuff.}Rửa chén và bóp vai cho em ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.21,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Oh, I also did the packaging.}A, tớ cũng đóng gói nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:05.89,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Next up is Dazai's. We made a cherry \Npound cake for his story "Cherries."}Tiếp theo là Dazai. \NBọn tớ làm bánh pound vị sơ ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.10,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I think this one tastes the best.}Tớ nghĩ món này vị ngon nhất.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:12.81,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{It's m-marbled? It's so pretty.}Đá cẩm thạch à? Đẹp quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:17.65,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{We used canned dark cherries and syrup \Nto add color. Well, my sister did.}Bọn tớ dùng sơ ri đen\N và si rô để tạo màu. Em gái tớ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:21.61,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{The next two are from the picture books\N}{\i1}{Swimmy}{\i0}{ and }{\i1}{Guri and Gura}{\i0}{.}Tiếp theo là từ hai cuốn sách ảnh \N"Swimmy" và "Guri và Gura".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.77,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{J-Just like in the b-books!}Y-Y chang trong sách kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:29.48,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Y-Your little sister is amazing.}E-Em gái cậu đỉnh quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:34.15,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{But see these bags? I picked them. \NI could use some praise, too, you know.}Còn cách đóng gói? Tớ làm đó, khen đi chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:37.26,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{N-Nukumizu, w-way to go.}N-Nukumizu, cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:41.51,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yes! I am the first-born son! \NSee what I can do when I put my mind to it?}Ồ! Vì tớ là con trai cả mà. \NĐã nghiêm túc thì phải thế chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:49.72,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur0.4\fs14\fnArial\b1\fscx90\3c&H4E5652&\c&H0B0C0A&\pos(421.333,259.999)}{Tsuwabuki Fest Is In}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:49.72,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fnArial\b1\fscx90\blur0.4\fs14\3c&H4E5652&\c&H0B0C0A&\pos(466.667,312.667)}{Days}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:44.22,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{So I guess we're good for the snacks.}Vậy xong vụ bánh kẹo nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:47.20,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{W-We also need recipes \Nand instructions with pictures.}C-Chúng ta cần công thức và ảnh nấu ăn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:49.30,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Okay, got it. I'll put those together.}Hiểu rồi. Để tớ tổng hợp lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:53.70,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{What are all those books?}Mấy cuốn sách gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:58.12,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-I got them from the public library. \NI have to return them today.}T-Tôi mượn ở thư viện nên giờ mang trả.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:05:00.31,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{How did you get so many of them here?}Sao mượn nhiều thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:02.63,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{B-Bit by bit.}M-Mượn từng lần một.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:05.83,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Th-The copy machine \Nhere at school is cheaper.}V-Vì máy copy ở trường rẻ mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.59,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{You just returned a bunch \Nand now you're borrowing more?}Trả hết và lại mượn nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:21.55,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I s-still need some to write the exhibit \Ndisplays. A-And some are for the rugrats.}V-Vẫn còn viết phần giới thiệu cho \Nbuổi triển lãm. V-Và cho lũ nhóc...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:25.38,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5\shad0\an8\b1\fs16\fnComic Sans MS\c&H53644B&\frx358\fry346\3c&HCEE0C6&\pos(246,258.667)}{The Very \NHungry\N Caterpillar}
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.55,0:05:25.38,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{If I don't read them stories before bed,\N th-they don't fall asleep.}Nếu không đọc truyện thì chúng sẽ không chịu ngủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.79,0:05:31.07,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{How are the articles for the displays going?}Mấy bài giới thiệu đến đâu rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:33.05,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-It'll take a little longer.}C-Chắc sẽ tốn thêm chút thời gian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:37.31,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{There are four of them, right? \NLet me write one of them.}Có 4 cái nhỉ? Để tớ viết một cái cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:41.82,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Y-You haven't finished your newsletter \Nmanuscript, bud. W-Write that!}C-Cậu còn chưa xong phần\N bản tin của mình mà? Viết đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:44.28,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Okay, I'll write that.}Ừm, tớ sẽ viết.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:50.09,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{What's wrong?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:52.16,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{G-Get your head down.}C-Cúi đầu xuống.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:03.01,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Um, maybe they were using \None of the third-floor study rooms.}Có lẽ họ dùng phòng học tầng 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:04.86,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{You know, to study for exams.}Để luyện thi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:12.60,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\blur1\bord0.5\shad0\b1\fs12\fax-0.35\fscx90\3c&HB8A4BF&\frz19.95\pos(402,200.667)}{Machinaka Plaza}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:17.08,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fax-0.65\fs8\c&H353832&\frz27.98\pos(378.666,202)}{Hitohito}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:17.08,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{N-Nukumizu, y-you're worried about me, right?}N-Nukumizu, cậu đang l-lo cho tôi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:20.72,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{A little. I didn't expect them\N to show up, so yeah.}Một chút. Không ngờ họ lại ở đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:24.93,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-I don't care. I-I know they're dating.}T-Tôi không sao. B-Biết họ đang hẹn hò mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:27.07,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Holding hands and stuff is normal.}Nắm tay cũng bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:31.16,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{E-Even at school, they're a-always together.}O-Ở trường họ cũng hay làm thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:35.78,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{But it's kind of different \Nwhen we're not at school.}Nhưng nó hơi khác khi ta không ở trường.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.70,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Outside, it's like they're \Nin an unfamiliar world.}Bên ngoài, họ cứ như đang ở thế giới khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:43.49,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Like they've found their own \Nspecial place to be together.}Cứ như ở thế giới của riêng họ vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:48.72,Default,Couple Girl,0,0,0,,{Hey, there's one more place \NI wanna check out. That okay?}Nè, còn mấy chỗ tớ muốn xem. Ghét qua nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:49.38,Default,Couple Boy,0,0,0,,{Sure.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:58.68,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{D-Don't get me wrong. I-I didn't hide\N because they were together.}Đ-Đừng có hiểu lầm. T-Tôi không\N trốn vì thấy họ bên nhau đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:02.80,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-It's because in f-first term, \NI would've been with them.}V-Vì trong học kì một... t-tôi đã luôn ở cùng họ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:07.28,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-I'm sad that I can't join them anymore.}T-Tôi cũng buồn khi không còn bên cạnh họ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:14.36,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Wh-When I joined the club in April, \Nth-they were both really nice to me.}H-Hồi mới tham gia CLB, h-họ rất tốt với tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:19.65,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{In c-class, I didn't have any friends. \NThey spent a bunch of time with me.}Trong lớp tôi không có bạn nên họ luôn cạnh tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:23.96,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Th-That was the first time \NI'd ever thought school was fun.}Đ-Đó là lần đầu tôi thấy đi học vui như vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:25.00,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\blur0.3\fax-0.65\fs8\c&H353832&\frz27.98\pos(378.666,202)}{Hitohito}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:28.61,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{B-But now, it's back to normal.}N-Nhưng bây giờ thì quay lại như ban đầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:36.62,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I'm sure Tsukinoki-senpai would take a \Nbreak from studying to see you anytime.}Tớ nghĩ chị Tsukinoki sẽ tranh\N thủ để gặp cậu khi có thể đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:38.18,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Y-Yeah.}Ừ-Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:41.16,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{And I don't think the prez\Nis trying to avoid you at all.}Và hội trưởng cũng không né tránh gì cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:50.53,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I know. B-But if I hadn't asked him out, maybe \Nwe th-three could've spent more time together.}Tôi biết. N-Nhưng nếu tôi không tỏ tình,\N thì có lẽ lúc này 3 người vẫn đang bên nhau...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:57.91,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{O-Once Tsuwabuki Fest is over,\N they'll both go away,}K-Khi lễ hội Tsuwabuki kết thúc, bọn họ sẽ rời đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:01.96,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{s-so I have to be able to get by on my own.}N-Nên tôi phải tự xoay sở.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:05.03,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{If you need anything from me,\N just say the word.}Nếu cần gì cứ nói ra nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:09.51,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-I can do it by myself.}T-Tôi có thể làm một mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:13.52,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I have to.}Vì tôi cần phải vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:17.18,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur0.4\fs14\fnArial\b1\fscx90\3c&H4E5652&\c&H0B0C0A&\pos(421.333,259.999)}{Tsuwabuki Fest Is In}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:17.18,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fnArial\b1\fscx90\blur0.4\fs14\3c&H4E5652&\c&H0B0C0A&\pos(466.667,312.667)}{Days}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:34.58,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{That's it for the pumpkin. \NNow I just need the bats.}Xong bí ngô, tiếp theo là dơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.58,Top,someone,0,0,0,,{You look so cute!}Dễ thương quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:38.36,Default,Girl Student,0,0,0,,{You're perfect in that,\N Karen-chan! It's super cute!}Dễ thương quá Keren-chan! Tuyệt ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:43.58,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Himemiya-san's something else.}Himemiya đỉnh ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:46.28,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{A demon is one thing, \Nbut she looks like a succubus.}Hoá trang thành ác quỷ mà cứ như succubus vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:47.50,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,Nuk-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.88,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Well? Are you scared?}Thế nào? Sợ không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:51.46,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{That's a lot of skin.}Hở hang quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:55.81,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yakishio, you shouldn't show your belly\N like that with people around.}Yakishio, tớ nghĩ cậu không nên khoe bụng đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:58.31,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{But this is how a mummy would look.}Nhưng xác ướp phải thế chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.83,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Wait. Hold on a second.}Khoan đã.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:03.81,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Are you naked under those bandages?}Cậu không mặc gì dưới lớp băng à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.89,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Well, yeah. Is that a problem?}Thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:07.31,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{I mean, everything's covered—}Thì tớ che hết rồi mà--
