Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.65,Default,Girl A,0,0,0,,{And out.}Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:10.88,Default,Girl B,0,0,0,,{Lemon, you're coming with us.}Lemon, lại đây nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:13.21,Top,Girl C,0,0,0,,{Hey, what do you boys think you're looking at?}Cậu nghĩ đám con trai sẽ nhìn vào đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:14.04,Default,Lemon,0,0,0,,{Huh? What's wrong with you all? Hey!}Hả? Mấy cậu bị gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.20,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Nukumizu-kun.}Nukumizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:18.72,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Look!}Nhìn nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.82,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Whaddaya think? Boo!}Thấy sao? Hù nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:22.70,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Um, you're cosplaying as a corpse?}Hoá trang thành xác chết hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:26.30,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{I'm a ghost! Have you ever seen\N a corpse looking this healthy?}Là ma! Thấy xác chết nào khoẻ mạnh vậy không?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:28.58,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I've never seen a ghost that healthy, either.}Tớ cũng không thấy con ma khoẻ mạnh bao giờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:29.90,Default,Nishikawa,0,0,0,,{Hey, Yanami.}Nè Yanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.57,Default,Nishikawa,0,0,0,,{Practice is starting.}Bắt đầu luyện tập thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:35.07,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,{Okay, on my way.}Ừm, tớ đi đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.06,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur0.4\fs14\fnArial\b1\fscx90\3c&H3B3741&\c&H000000&\pos(421.333,259.999)}{Tsuwabuki Fest Is In}
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.06,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur0.4\fs14\fnArial\b1\fscx90\3c&H7898B1&\c&H0B0C0A&\pos(421.333,259.999)\clip(m 300 282 l 492 238 530 268)}{Tsuwabuki Fest Is In}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.06,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fnArial\b1\fscx90\blur0.4\fs14\3c&H4E5652&\c&H0B0C0A&\pos(468.667,292.667)}{Days}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:49.26,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{So you wrote a continuation \Nof the story you wrote at camp?}Em viết tiếp câu chuyện đã viết ở trại hè à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.73,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yeah, more or less.}Vâng. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.76,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{And Koto wrote something new.}Koto thì đang viết tác phẩm mới.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:55.48,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yeah, but this one doesn't \Nhave any dirty scenes.}Vâng, nhưng lần này không có cảnh bậy bạ đâu nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:57.64,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I think she finally caught on about that.}Em nghĩ có lẽ chị ấy biết có anh đọc qua.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:10:00.20,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{I wish she'd catch on to some other things, too.}Anh mong cậu ấy cũng biết giữ ý tứ ở mất việc khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:04.85,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, it sounds like Komari-chan's \Nhaving trouble with the display articles.}Có vẻ Komari đang gặp rắc rối \Nở mấy bài giới thiệu nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:07.91,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I keep telling her I'm willing to help...}Vâng, em đã nói sẽ giúp đỡ nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:09.88,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{Emergency!}Khẩn cấp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:11.67,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{It's Komari-chan!}Là Komari-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:14.13,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\fs14\bord0\blur0.3\shad0\fscx95\fax-0.2\pos(383.333,102.667)\frz308.1\frx8\fry10\c&H5F5F95&}{The Complete Works \Nof Dazai Osamu}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:22.60,Default,Konuki,0,0,0,,{She'll be fine. She's just needs sleep.\N Nothing to worry about.}Con bé không sao, chỉ thiếu ngủ thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.34,0:10:24.55,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Komari-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:30.26,Default,Konuki,0,0,0,,{I know you go through a lot at your age,\Ntrying to push yourselves to your limits.}Cô biết các em đang độ tuổi sung sức, \Ncố gắng vượt qua giới hạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:35.11,Default,Konuki,0,0,0,,{I had experiences like that, too.}Ngày xưa cô cũng thế mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.61,Default,Konuki,0,0,0,,{Wanna hear the story?}Muốn nghe không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.36,Top,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Uh, no thanks.}À thôi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:39.74,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I think I'm good.}Em cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.92,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,Sao mình lại ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:53.09,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,Nukumizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:56.83,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Y-Ya dumbbell. That one's the cauliflower.}Đ-Đồ ngốc. Đó là súp lơ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:58.69,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{What the heck is she dreaming about?}Cậu ta đang mơ cái quái gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:15.93,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Wha—}Cái--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:19.03,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,M-Mắc gì cậu ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:23.88,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Konuki-sensei brought you home. \NI came along to show her the way.}Cô Konuki đưa cậu về. Tớ chỉ đường.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:26.41,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{K-Konuki-sensei, huh?}Cô Konuki à...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:30.79,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{P-Pajamas?!}Đ-Đồ ngủ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.28,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yeah, Konuki-sensei changed \Nyou out of your clothes.}Cô Konuki thay cho cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:34.57,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{D-Did you look?}C-Cậu thấy rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:35.75,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I did not look.}Không có...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:38.95,Default,Konuki,0,0,0,,{Aw, you didn't even look? What a shame.}Em không thấy à? Tiếc ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:41.93,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Sensei, there are small children present.}Cô à, đang có trẻ nhỏ kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:45.63,Default,Shin,0,0,0,,{Are you my sister's boyfriend?}Anh là bạn trai của chị em hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.17,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{No, I'm not.}Không phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:50.42,Default,Shin,0,0,0,,{Then are you her friend?}Vậy là bạn?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:54.52,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Um, we're just in the same club together...}Ừm, bọn anh chỉ chung CLB...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:59.25,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Yes, we're friends.}À ừm, là bạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:04.67,Default,Shin,0,0,0,,{Hina, see? He's big sis's friend.\N Don't be scared.}Hina, bạn của chị kìa. Không phải sợ đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:16.56,Default,Hina,0,0,0,,{Just like big sis.}Y chang chị hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.96,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh? Yeah, it looks cute.}Hả? À ừm dễ thương.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.05,Italics,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Huh? What is this adorable creature?}Cái sinh vật dễ thương này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:29.64,Default,Konuki,0,0,0,,{All right, I'll watch over your brother \Nand sister, so please enjoy yourselves.}Vậy thì để cô trông hai đứa em cho, cứ từ từ nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:40.18,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Hey, Komari. Why don't you send me \Nwhat you've written for the displays so far?}Nè Komari, gửi tớ xem mấy bản thảo xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.36,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Wh-Why?}T-Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:44.56,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{You can't keep pushing yourself like this.}Cậu không thể cứ cố quá sức như vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:45.82,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{B-But...}N-Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:47.99,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{You should rest and let me do the—}Cậu nên nghỉ ngơi và để tớ--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.41,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I-I'll finish them!}T-Tôi sẽ hoàn thành chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:55.98,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{I'll finish them. J-Just let me do the writing.}Tôi sẽ viết hết. Đ-Để tôi viết.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:12:59.92,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{When will you be done?}Khi nào thì xong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.73,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{B-By tomorrow morning.}S-Sáng mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:07.59,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Okay. When you're done, \Nsend the data to everyone in the club.}Hiểu rồi, khi nào xong thì \Ngửi dữ liệu cho mọi người nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:09.93,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Th-Thanks.}C-Cảm ơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:12.95,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{But in exchange, I want you \Nto promise me something.}Nhưng đổi lại, hứa với tớ một chuyện.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:14.95,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{Promise you?}Hứa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:17.62,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Let us handle everything else for the exhibit.}Để bọn tớ xử lý mọi chuyện của buổi triển lãm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:19.94,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{You stay home tomorrow and get some rest.}Ngày mai cậu sẽ nghỉ tịnh dưỡng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:22.73,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{If you do, I'll let you finish writing.}Nếu chịu hứa thì tớ sẽ cho cậu viết.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:25.26,Default,Komari,0,0,0,,{B-But we have to set up tomorrow.}N-Nhưng ngày mai phải chuẩn bị nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:28.89,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{Well, maybe you should let me show\N what I can do just this once.}Cứ để tớ ra vẻ ngầu lần này đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:32.70,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{How was Komari-chan?}Komari sao rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.22,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{She seemed better after she got some sleep.}Có vẻ khá hơn sau khi ngủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:36.60,Default,Tamaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, good.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:42.05,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{We want her to still have fun \Nat school even after we're gone.}Bọn chị muốn con bé vui vẻ\N ngay cả sau khi rời khỏi đây...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:46.04,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{We wanted the literature club to \Nbecome a place where she'd belong.}Muốn CLB văn học thành nơi con bé thuộc về.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:48.13,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,{And we've been trying to watch over her...}Và cố gắng ở xa dõi theo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:53.17,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{You told me before that you want \Nto help Komari get stronger.}Chị nói muốn giúp Komari trở nên mạnh mẽ hơn nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:54.93,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{But you know what?}Nhưng mà cậu ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:14:02.27,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord3\shad0\blur0.4\fs14\fnArial\b1\fscx90\3c&H96A798&\c&H0B0C0A&\pos(421.333,259.999)}{Tsuwabuki Fest Is In}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:14:02.27,Default,text,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fnArial\b1\fscx90\blur0.4\fs14\3c&H4E5652&\c&H0B0C0A&\pos(468,292)}{Days}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:14:00.87,Default,Nukumizu,0,0,0,,{I think she's a little stronger than you think.}Em nghĩ đã mạnh mẽ hơn hai người nghĩ rồi.
